    "name": "100 Find Kitties: Thief",
    "steam_appid": 3333680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333680/extras/f326e115615fd4cf83df71e21e40be50.avif?t=1771688773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333680/extras_big/f326e115615fd4cf83df71e21e40be50.avif?t=1771688773 width=800 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >警告 ！ Triple C 游戏（可爱舒适的猫）警告！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了得到它们最喜欢的猫零食的钱，猫几乎会做任何事，它们甚至准备犯罪。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些可爱的毛茸茸的小偷闯入了整个星球上守卫最森严的堡垒，里面装满了金钱、黄金和艺术品。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这些偷猫贼偷走你的东西之前，帮助他们抓住他们。喵！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏的猫：小偷是一款隐藏物品/隐藏生物游戏。玩家的任务是找到地图上的一百只猫。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用大气的手绘图形装饰，小猫们安逸又友善。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333680/extras/aedc3eb6c703f3ee24b5f585d196b293.avif?t=1771688773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333680/extras_big/aedc3eb6c703f3ee24b5f585d196b293.avif?t=1771688773 width=800 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100只可爱的猫 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100只橡皮鸡 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4个隐藏的文物 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图上的互动元素 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘图形</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333680/extras/dab3682c4fb4ed8c307fc806a630786c.avif?t=1771688773\" width=558 height=179 /></span></p>",
